@startuml
title Rental Status Lifecycle (Detailed Version)

' == USER BORROWING PROCESS ==

APPROVED --> CANCELED : User canceled the request
note right of APPROVED
Triggered by:
• User cancels before picking up the car  
• System updates BorrowRequest and Rental records  
• Car remains AVAILABLE for other users
end note

APPROVED --> ACTIVE : User borrowed the car
note left of ACTIVE
Triggered by:
• User picks up the car  
• Rental officially starts  
• System marks car as "in use"
end note

ACTIVE --> FINISHED : User returned the car
note right of FINISHED
Triggered by:
• User returns the car  
• System closes the rental and updates car availability
end note

@enduml
